Adding a new language:
execute the following command (via terminal) in the project directory:
        lupdate -pro BrotherDSmobile720D.pro -ts German.ts

Create translations with QtLinguist and then execute the following command:
        lrelease German.ts

move the German.qm file to /home/[user]/.config/QtScanImage/languages/
then the language should appear in the language selection
